data.description: This designer upper-level unit will impress you with gorgeous hardwood floors that gleam throughout the sun-drenched rooms! The updated kitchen has top of the line stainless steel appliances, ceiling-high cabinets and beautiful countertops and backsplash. The floor plan is an open flow from the kitchen to the dining area and living room for effortless entertaining. Sliders open up to the super private west-facing deck with glorious sunset views. The large and lovely bedroom has a designer ceiling fan and large walk-in closet. Full bath with extra hand-held shower combo. At the end of the day enjoy the amazing amenities of the desirable Mountainview complex, including pool, clubhouse, tot lot and more. Great for commuters with close proximity to the NYS Thruway and Tappan Zee Bridge. Seize this outstanding unit before it's gone!
